<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>.. بِهِذَا وَمَا يَجْرِي صَحِيحُ الدَّفَاتِرِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>وَهَلْ نَافِعٌ لِلْمُجْرِمِينَ اعْتِذَارُهُمْ<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>إِذَا دَارَ يَوْمَ الْجَمْعِ سُوءُ الدَّوَائِرِ<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>وَقَالَ الشَّقِيُّ الْمُفْتَرِي كُنْتُ كَارِهاً<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span>ضَعِيفاً مُضَاعاً بَيْنَ تِلْكَ الْعَسَاكِرِ<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>أَمَانِيَّ تَلْقَاهَا لِكُلِّ مُتَبَّرٍ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>حَقِيقَتُهَا نَبْذُ الْهُدَى وَالشَّعَائِرِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>تَعُودُ سَرَاباً بَعْدَ مَا كَانَ لامِعاً<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>لِكُلِّ جَهُولٍ فِي الْمَهَامهِ حَائِرِ<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>فَإِنْ شِئْتَ أَنْ تُحَضْى بِكُلِّ فَضِيلَةٍ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>وَتَظْهَرَ فِي ثَوْبٍ مِنْ الْمَجْدِ بَاهِرِ<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span>وَتَدْنُوا مِنْ الْجَبَّارِ جَلَّ جَلالُهُ<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p13"></span>إِلى غَايَةٍ فَوْقَ الْعُلَى وَالْمَظَاهِرِ<a href="#p13" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p14"></span>فَهَاجِرْ إِلى رَبِّ الْبَرِيَّةِ طَالِباً<a href="#p14" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p15"></span>رِضَاهُ وَرَاغِمْ بِالْهُدَى كُلَّ جَائِرِ<a href="#p15" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p16"></span>وَجَانِبِ سَبِيلَ الْعَادِلِينَ بِرَبِّهِمْ<a href="#p16" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p17"></span>ذَوِي الشِّرْكِ وَالتَّعْطِيلِ مَعَ كُلِّ غَادِرِ<a href="#p17" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p18"></span>وَبَادِرْ إِلى رَفْعِ الشِّكَايَةِ ضَارِعاً<a href="#p18" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p19"></span>إِلى كَاشِفِ الْبَلْوَى عَلِيمِ السَّرَائِرِ<a href="#p19" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p20"></span>وَكَابِدْ إِلى أنْ تَبَلُغَ النَّفْسُ عُذْرَهَا<a href="#p20" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p21"></span>وَتُرْفَعَ فِي ثَوْب مِن الْعَفْوِ سَاتِرِ<a href="#p21" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>